thread.title_full: Mouser Electronics reviewed by Robert T

author: Robert T
title: Robert T
text: I was looking for a 2N2955 pnp power transistor in TO3 case but apparently that isn't a good number any more. Your site gave me the option of looking for an equivalent device using the specs for the complimentary device (2N3055 npn TO3) which helped very much. I ordered 2 of MJ2955G.
